{"tid":337222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友老母生日，買咩好？","createTime":"2017-07-27T06:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T19:20:32.000Z","uid":109650,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b3fb04720c47a079f24ae1a5c23419e794cba88","tid":337222,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:19:13.000Z","msg":"佢呀媽就快生日，男朋友話帶埋我去睇show，開開心心玩一日，又強調唔洗買禮物， 話之前已經買咗好多，佢呀媽會唔好意思，唔通真係唔洗買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （其實我同佢呀媽相處得極唔自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n-<br />\n本身母親節買左禮物畀佢呀媽<br />\n中秋又買左酒店月餅，諗住印象好啲<br />\n前前後後用左千幾到啦<br />\n（男朋友係我屋企人生日同節目都係得個講字最後冇買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n-<br />\n而家佢呀媽幾鐘意我，我覺得都唔會話肉赤既，始終呢啲人情世故，門面功夫都要做既，問題係而家佢生日照計係比節日重要既， 咁應該更加要送生日禮物，但之前兩次都送過我又唔想再洗咁多錢，同埋八月紀念日，再九月我本身要去旅行，十一月就我男朋友生日都冇咁多錢可用落去佢呀媽生日度<br />\n-<br />\n結論係：<br />\n佢呀媽係做緊飲食業<br />\n肥同矮，不化妝<br />\n預 $200-400 到<br />\n有咩介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f893ff072274b8b62767c6aee4bc4938e8681c29","tid":337222,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"百佳禮卷 <br />\n肯定人人啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795423d7f400ab1d98eac1db5461a6561258467c","tid":337222,"uid":117901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"請食飯咪得"},{"pid":"194a147056eb8667acb27711491fffb71ca2f04d","tid":337222,"uid":34877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"海味/護膚/養生野 平貴自己揀"},{"pid":"9d4f5a48b1a3f13479a45bed9e90458edecbf920","tid":337222,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T06:53:27.000Z","msg":"鐘"},{"pid":"6ec4cca158d583770a12ecacb0af3dafea35ca24","tid":337222,"uid":40272,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"女朋友老母：「快來幹我..我..我要..我要懷上你的孩子..快射在我裡面」<br />\n這個時候我也快受不了，決定加速衝刺，用飛快的速度不斷的抽插伯母，她也似乎感受到我的衝勁，早就叫到歇斯底裡了，終於在插了百來下後，我將老二頂到子宮，然後將所有的精液都射在伯母的陰道裡，可是我並不打算罷休，又開始用力的抽插她‧"},{"pid":"f93d06b25c51652fd894133c51beaaa07d1a7f38","tid":337222,"uid":125773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"蛋"},{"pid":"2f4fb11515a6167dffb676abaafc09f1075af4de","tid":337222,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:58:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百佳禮卷 <br />\n肯定人人啱用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好師奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過諗得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313808dce106132154ae8deb632ca5c9a007ee9b","tid":337222,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請食飯咪得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪仲貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b2f594c4a6c16445a3da190d99fd3d859e0229","tid":337222,"uid":109650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:58:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鐘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n鐘柒你老母"},{"pid":"ec8443e0930ae24233dcfe4e28f505727bfbfeb6","tid":337222,"uid":13996,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"送個孫比佢"},{"pid":"5ba2446add013fb9449ed0148230a514d788f6a3","tid":337222,"uid":79145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:26:43.000Z","msg":"增高丸+減肥茶"},{"pid":"8f2e9fd24095ee699aeec553ec8114b87439cd85","tid":337222,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>增高丸+減肥茶</blockquote><br />\n想俾人屌死都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae034551f30e56c999fb2bee8455676dd80e54e","tid":337222,"uid":54234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:34